    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《世外桃源》是一款2D精致像素风的模拟经营+供应链+自动化+恋爱养成的游戏.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>我和美术Mofei两个人不间断的制作了7年才完成了该游戏的大部分内容的制作.希望您能喜欢本游戏.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >   <strong>*游戏本体支持中英日,可以在创意工坊额外订阅语言包,目前支持:法语,西语,德语,土耳其语,韩语,俄语,葡萄牙语(巴西).</strong>     </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>还在传统种地吗?来试试招募村民帮你自动化产出农作物!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/281ff9425f8e145de02e25dc815bc334.avif?t=1771926566\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras_big/281ff9425f8e145de02e25dc815bc334.avif?t=1771926566 width=800 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>手动种地=&gt;种植园=&gt;温室</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/13ba31a32781351913d625732bdd8521.poster.avif?t=1771926566\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/13ba31a32781351913d625732bdd8521.webm?t=1771926566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/13ba31a32781351913d625732bdd8521.mp4?t=1771926566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>打造属于你的生机勃勃的农场</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/da1e30fb7d18fd9c216c288935f6ff7f.avif?t=1771926566\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras_big/da1e30fb7d18fd9c216c288935f6ff7f.avif?t=1771926566 width=800 height=372 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>动物小屋产出牛奶+茶圃产出的茶叶=&gt;&gt;在商业街出售奶茶</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/72689f291d17b8dd2a603253627fc4b6.poster.avif?t=1771926566\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/72689f291d17b8dd2a603253627fc4b6.webm?t=1771926566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/72689f291d17b8dd2a603253627fc4b6.mp4?t=1771926566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>在商业街打造属于你的繁华商业小镇</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/bced51dd45b045fd4bbc695229cee5f8.avif?t=1771926566\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/917ea23f9b8add8a4f11ef3f5160acb6.poster.avif?t=1771926566\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/917ea23f9b8add8a4f11ef3f5160acb6.webm?t=1771926566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/917ea23f9b8add8a4f11ef3f5160acb6.mp4?t=1771926566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>5个可追求女性对象和4个可追求男性对象</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/5ced041a22eb8856e82059d1590c1a93.avif?t=1771926566\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras_big/5ced041a22eb8856e82059d1590c1a93.avif?t=1771926566 width=800 height=606 /></span><i>8个商业建筑,11个农场建筑,4个后山建筑,150余种独特供应链体系,维持好供应链是一门技术活~</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/f3541bf6310dca333b06a479269549eb.poster.avif?t=1771926566\" width=800 height=502 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/f3541bf6310dca333b06a479269549eb.webm?t=1771926566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/f3541bf6310dca333b06a479269549eb.mp4?t=1771926566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>布置独属于你的温馨小家!高度自定义的瓦片地图系统允许玩家自己布置墙体,地板,壁纸,灯饰和家具.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/5cee052f7145fd97b836d9d7345c07e3.avif?t=1771926566\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras_big/5cee052f7145fd97b836d9d7345c07e3.avif?t=1771926566 width=800 height=712 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>50余种独特收藏品每一种都会提供独特的不可思议的效果,比如可以不消耗种子或是提升村民的工作效率~</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/85085ac60bd9f65a5cd83d84d7a9f924.poster.avif?t=1771926566\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/85085ac60bd9f65a5cd83d84d7a9f924.webm?t=1771926566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/85085ac60bd9f65a5cd83d84d7a9f924.mp4?t=1771926566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085890/extras/86b55f78ca1475fe265625124cfc3004.avif?t=1771926566\" width=944 height=540 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>丰富的闲暇生活,让你的农场生活慢下来,享受每一天~</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我的朋友,希望您可以在世外桃源找到独属于你的田园旅程~衷心感谢您的支持!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>EA阶段工作计划和开发进度</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >节日:中秋节 (2024/9/9已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >节日:端午节 (2024/9/17已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >功能:日历 (2024/9/17已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >功能:以瓦片地图的形式布置自宅场景,允许自定义墙体,地板和墙纸 (2024/11/27已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >功能:多存档读取系统,允许玩家同时拥有多个不同栏位的存档 (2024/12/5已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >功能:任务系统,任务布告栏 (2024/12/10已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >功能:新手引导任务 (2024/12/10已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海边场景 (2025/1/30已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩法:钓鱼 (2025/1/30已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩法,场景:水族馆,允许玩家将获得的鱼获和水产以各种不同形式的鱼缸布置到水族馆中,通过收取门票来获得收益 <i><strong>(</strong></i>2025/4/11已完成<i><strong>)</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重做玩家自宅初始小木屋外形(阶段1),重做供应链配方解锁书的UI,重做传送符的UI(2025/4/23已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城镇别墅的内部预制装修(2025/5/22已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创意工坊支持,订阅和上传立绘/数值Mod/多语言Mod,本地Mod管理器(2025/5/29已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海边的建筑物和供应链:晒盐场,养殖场,打捞站,海景餐厅(2025/7/14已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新村民社区系统,城镇村民建筑物完全重做,可以以鸟瞰图视图建造,管理村民建筑和相关功能建筑.新增学校,诊所,社区活动中心和食堂等功能建筑物.新增道路系统和路灯绿化等美化功能.(2025/10/3已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海边的美化,游客,烧烤摊,烧烤经营游戏.(2026/1/10已完成)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正在制作项目:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角小人的换装系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角小人的肤色,头发,眼睛颜色自定义</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城镇新增针对主角服务的理发店,服装店等新建筑物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等待制作(部分顺序会有变化,并不是严格按照顺序来的,但是大概是这个制作流程):</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自宅内部更多的墙体,灯,家具,地板</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女神山洞的美化和新功能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >农场地图更多皮肤(竹林,峡谷等)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海景甜品店,海边饮料摊</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随版本更新,一直持续优化的部分:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多的人物剧情,保证每个固定村民都至少有2个个人好感度剧情</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手柄支持(目前已完成95%)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作和玩法上的优化</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多的菜谱,供应链,特定村民的隐藏配方等(需要等待美术老师Mofei的配合)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FAQ/开发者的话</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我很喜欢模拟经营游戏,于是在很多年前萌生了做一款游戏的想法.我们遇到了非常多的困难,但幸好,最后我们都一一克服了.我和Mofei在这个游戏里倾注了非常多的感情和精力.如果有什么做的不够好的地方请通过各种方式告诉我,我会定期查看steam讨论组的问题并进行回答,有任何问题和建议都请及时向我反馈,谢谢你~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >联系方式:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏交流qq群:166716221</p>",
